# FBA Admin Backend

Generated by `fbago init [[ .Module ]] --template [[ .TemplateModule ]]`.

## Layout

- `cmd/api`: HTTP entrypoint.
- `internal/app/admin`: project-owned admin module.
- `internal/app/config`: project-owned system config module.
- `internal/app/dict`: project-owned dictionary module.
- `internal/app/notice`: project-owned notice module.
- `plugins/email`: project-owned email captcha plugin reference.
- `plugins/oauth2`: project-owned OAuth2 login plugin reference.
- `plugins/task`: project-owned task scheduler plugin reference.
- `.env`: local defaults. Real system environment variables override this file.

## Commands

```bash
make tidy
make test
make build
make run
go run ./cmd/api migrate up
go run ./cmd/api migrate status
```

When using a local development build of `fbago`, the generated `go.mod`
includes a local `replace` for `github.com/yuWorm/fba-go`. Installed builds can
use `fbago init ... --core-replace /path/to/fba-go` or `FBAGO_CORE_REPLACE`.
